'P' pawn       
'K' king      

'W' wazir      W    soil               
'F' ferz       F    air                
'N' knight     N    horse              
'R' rook       W*   tower      (composed of soil/rocks)
'B' bishop     F*   heaven             
'U' unicorn    N*   myth               

'V' veggie     W F = soil air
'T' tapir      W N = soil horse
'C' cardinal   W B = heaven's soil (rock on which to build the church)
'L' golem      W N*= soil myth          
'G' giraffe    F N = air horse          
'S' spire      F W*= air tower          
'X' phoenix    F N*= air myth           
'J' trojan     N W*= horse building     
'D' death      N F*= heaven horse       
'Q' queen      W*F*= tower to heaven (ruler by divine mandate)
'A' akupara    W*N*= tower myth         
'Z' zeus       F*N*= heaven myth        

